                <h2 class="font-medium xl:pt-3 line-clamp-2 2xl:line-clamp-none sm:text-xl xl:text-2xl"><a href="/single/Index/ARTL000063731">國宴裡的台灣味</a></h2>
                <p class="text-lora text-grey mb-1 xl:mb-1 py-1 xl:py-1 text-xs xl:text-base">June 09, 2016 </p>
                <p class="line text-justify text-sm xl:text-base 2xl:text-lg">
